    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/69c7e571433f5ddb3197f25d6bd4e9d6.avif?t=1733561640\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Cambur: The Sacred Orbs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the Fruitiverse in <i>Super Cambur: The Sacred Orbs</i>, a classic turn-based RPG inspired by the golden age of the genre. Join Cambur, the fearless banana warrior, and a quirky band of fruity heroes as they embark on an epic quest to recover the Sacred Orbs and thwart a mysterious villain threatening their juicy world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍌 <strong>Classic Turn-Based Combat:</strong> Relive the timeless thrill of strategic battles, where every move counts. Plan your attacks, manage resources, and unleash powerful abilities to outwit your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/e37ab00fe8a4ec9c3d5f89b01d254090.poster.avif?t=1733561640\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/e37ab00fe8a4ec9c3d5f89b01d254090.webm?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/e37ab00fe8a4ec9c3d5f89b01d254090.mp4?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>🍌 <strong>Rich, Nostalgic Storytelling:</strong> Immerse yourself in a heartfelt and humorous tale filled with unforgettable characters, charming dialogue, and unexpected twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/992dc7c053a22c9bea1321692dba9a5f.poster.avif?t=1733561640\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/992dc7c053a22c9bea1321692dba9a5f.webm?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/992dc7c053a22c9bea1321692dba9a5f.mp4?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>🍌 <strong>Vibrant World to Explore:</strong> Travel through lush jungles, crystalline caverns, and mystical temples, each brimming with secrets, puzzles, and treasures waiting to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/fb20c6276e52be9d4524a5584b29ed95.poster.avif?t=1733561640\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/fb20c6276e52be9d4524a5584b29ed95.webm?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/fb20c6276e52be9d4524a5584b29ed95.mp4?t=1733561640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>🍌 <strong>Fruitastic Party System:</strong> Build your dream team of fruity warriors, each with unique skills and customizable abilities to suit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras/c6282817a2dae270315708190ba3b434.avif?t=1733561640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329840/extras_big/c6282817a2dae270315708190ba3b434.avif?t=1733561640 width=800 height=448 /></span> <br>🍌 <strong>Pixel-Perfect Art Style:</strong> Enjoy beautifully detailed pixel art and animations that bring the Fruitiverse to life with a modern twist on retro aesthetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br>🍌 <strong>Memorable Soundtrack:</strong> Lose yourself in an enchanting soundtrack that captures the spirit of classic RPG adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to peel back the layers of an epic adventure? The Sacred Orbs hold the key to saving the Fruitiverse, and it’s up to you to unite the fruits and defeat the looming darkness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
